code>point3</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The first point of the second line segment.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>point4</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The second point of the second line segment.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>intersectionPoint</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This is set to the intersection\npoint if an intersection is detected.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">True if an intersection is detected, false otherwise.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineIntersect(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineIntersect(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Common_LineTools_LineIntersect_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__'>LineIntersect(Vector2F, Vector2F, Vector2F, Vector2F, out Vector2F)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Common/LineTools.cs#L314'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This method detects if two line segments intersect,\nand, if so, the point of intersection.\nNote: If two line segments are coincident, then\nno intersection is detected (there are actually\ninfinite intersection points).</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static bool LineIntersect(Vector2F point1, Vector2F point2, Vector2F point3, Vector2F point4, out Vector2F intersectionPoint)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>point1</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The first point of the first line segment.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>point2</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The second point of the first line segment.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>point3</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The first point of the second line segment.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>point4</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The second point of the second line segment.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>intersectionPoint</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">This is set to the intersection\npoint if an intersection is detected.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">True if an intersection is detected, false otherwise.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineIntersect2(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineIntersect2(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Common_LineTools_LineIntersect2_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__'>LineIntersect2(ref Vector2F, ref Vector2F, ref Vector2F, ref Vector2F, out Vector2F)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Common/LineTools.cs#L84'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Check if the lines a0-&gt;a1 and b0-&gt;b1 cross.\nIf they do, intersectionPoint will be filled\nwith the point of crossing.\nGrazing lines should not return true.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static bool LineIntersect2(ref Vector2F a0, ref Vector2F a1, ref Vector2F b0, ref Vector2F b1, out Vector2F intersectionPoint)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>a0</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>a1</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>b0</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>b1</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>intersectionPoint</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineSegmentAabbIntersect(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Aabb)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineSegmentAabbIntersect(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Aabb)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Common_LineTools_LineSegmentAabbIntersect_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Aabb_'>LineSegmentAabbIntersect(ref Vector2F, ref Vector2F, Aabb)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Common/LineTools.cs#L347'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Get all intersections between a line segment and an AABB.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static Vertices LineSegmentAabbIntersect(ref Vector2F point1, ref Vector2F point2, Aabb aabb)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>point1</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The first point of the line segment to test</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>point2</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The second point of the line segment to test.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>aabb</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Aabb.html'>Aabb</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The AABB that is used for testing intersection.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Vertices.html'>Vertices</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineSegmentVerticesIntersect(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Vertices)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.LineSegmentVerticesIntersect(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Vertices)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Common_LineTools_LineSegmentVerticesIntersect_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__Alis_Core_Physic_Common_Vertices_'>LineSegmentVerticesIntersect(ref Vector2F, ref Vector2F, Vertices)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Common/LineTools.cs#L326'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Get all intersections between a line segment and a list of vertices\nrepresenting a polygon. The vertices reuse adjacent points, so for example\nedges one and two are between the first and second vertices and between the\nsecond and third vertices. The last edge is between vertex vertices.Count - 1\nand verts0. (ie, vertices from a Geometry or AABB)</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static Vertices LineSegmentVerticesIntersect(ref Vector2F point1, ref Vector2F point2, Vertices vertices)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>point1</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The first point of the line segment to test</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>point2</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F.html'>Vector2F</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The second point of the line segment to test.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>vertices</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Vertices.html'>Vertices</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.LineTools.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The vertices, as described above</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Vertices.html'>Vertices</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
